caption: French Sauces
tags: cuisine
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The five //mother sauces// of classical French cooking — Béchamel, Velouté, Espagnole, Sauce Tomat, and Hollandaise — form the basis of hundreds of derived sauces.  Mastering them unlocks most of the classical French repertoire.
